All Implemented Interfaces:
Command, ProgressReporting
public final class KnnSimsCommand
extends SortEventsCommand

Task that read in a file and produces the k-nearest-neighbors for each base entry. Assumes the file is composed of entry, entry, weight triples that are delimited by tabs.

Author:
Hamish I A Morgan <hamish.morgan@sussex.ac.uk>
